phantom class
-----------------

class used only for extending a style

%button {     //denoted by starting a % symbol
		padding: 10px;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: blue;
		border-radius: 6px;
}


consumed by
.buy {
	@extend %button;       ==== .buy{padding: 10px;font-weight: bold;background: blue;border-radius: 6px;}
}
